data.description: This Vehicle-Lover’s DREAM property offers a beautifully renovated cottage, a 2400 sqft garage/shop and attractive landscaping. The house presents custom cabinetry and countertops, engineered hardwoods and crown molding throughout. As you enter the rear door, you are greeted by the breakfast/kitchen area. The kitchen boasts granite countertops, with newer appliances, garbage disposal, and under cabinet lighting. As you walk to the left, you you will enter a cozy living room with ample seating, along with a fireplace. As you go right, the laundry room will be on your left. Both bedrooms have ample closet space, and ceiling fans throughout. The bathroom is totally renovated, and has a tub/shower combo. Outside to the right you’ll find a pavilion nestled under the many mature trees, a privacy fence, and ample turning/parking area for even the longest of trailers. The garage has 220-amp service, a separate established internet account, a 9000 lb vehicle lift, office area, bathroom, HVAC, and 800+ sqft of storage on the second story. This no HOA neighborhood is located on the northside of Spartanburg, 2 minutes from Spartanburg Regional Hospital, restaurants and grocery stores, and just 5 minutes from everything that downtown has to offer.
